data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated rancher, ideally situated on over an acre of land in Gloucester Point. Ideal for commuters to the Peninsula, Williamsburg, Yorktown, and Hampton, this home offers both convenience and comfort. Step inside to discover 7 well-appointed rooms, including 3 bdrms and 2 full baths, all updated to modern standards. The interior features a charming brick fireplace, creating a cozy focal point in the living space. The attached garage provides convenient parking and storage options. Recent updates include bamboo flooring, new windows, encapsulated crawl space with dehumidifier and new heat pump in the last few years, ensuring efficient and reliable heating and cooling. Outside, the well-landscaped yard is a true oasis, complete with a greenhouse and several sheds, offering ample storage and gardening opportunities. Above ground pool. Additionally, there's a 20 x 20 shed with underground electricity, providing even more utility and convenience.
